{"word":"συμφύω","slug":"συμφύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμφύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-φύσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make to grow together</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>συμπέφῡκα</el>, aor2 <el>συνέφῡν</el>:— <i>to grow together</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to grow to</i> or <i>into</i>, <el>ς. ἀλλήλοις</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to grow up with one, to become natural</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}